00:33:51,929 --> 00:33:54,523
I'm talking a big mother
with big beady eyes.

471
00:33:54,565 --> 00:33:57,261
-Kind of looks like... Right?
-Just like that.

472
00:33:57,301 --> 00:33:59,496
Looks at the guy, right in the eyes,
and he says,

473
00:33:59,537 --> 00:34:03,997
"Hey, brother, you looking for me?"
Voice over.

474
00:34:04,542 --> 00:34:06,976
"Ever wonder why life wasn't this easy?

475
00:34:07,011 --> 00:34:11,038
"At Crest and Landing, transferring
multiple loans to one company

